About

Michelle Vieth is a 44 year old Mexican Actress. Born Michelle Jacqueline Vieth Paetau on 19th November, 1979 in Marshalltown, Iowa, USA, she is famous for her roles as Julia Gonzalez/Julio Gonzalez in the Televisa telenovela Mi Pequeña Traviesa, Lucía de la Macorra/Adriana de la Macorra in the Televisa telenovela Soñadoras, Paola Montero in the Televisa telenovela Mujeres engañadas, Laura González in the Televisa juvenile telenovela Amigas y Rivales, Nadia Castillo Bojórquez in the Canal de las Estrellas telenovela Clase 406, Vivian Sousa de San Román in the Canal de las Estrellas telenovela La madrastra, Karen Farias Rivas del Castillo in the Televisa telenovela Mundo de fieras, Pilar in the Canal de las Estrellas telenovela Al diablo con los guapos, Michelle Phillips in the Telemundo/RTI Colombia telenovela La traición, Ana Julia Villaseñor in the Televisa telenovela Cuidado con el ángel, Daniela de la Vega Quijano in the TV Azteca telenovela La otra cara del alma, and Fernanda Diez Acuña in the Las Estrellas telenovela Mi fortuna es amarte in a career that spans 1995–present and 1997-present. Her zodiac sign is Scorpio.

Michelle Vieth has been in 3 on-screen matchups, including Arath de la Torre in Amigas y rivales (2001), Héctor Soberón in Mi pequeña traviesa (1997) and Mauricio Aspe in Stepmother (2005).
